          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Fairness to Pet Owners Act of 2018 </b></p> <p>This bill directs the Federal Trade Commission to require a&nbsp;prescriber&nbsp;of a household-animal&nbsp;medication to&nbsp;provide a free copy of the prescription to the&nbsp;pet owner before offering to fill the prescription and without the pet owner having to request a copy.</p>]]></text>
